ed="T" n="0809a11"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0809a11"/><head><date from-iso="+0907-06-10" key="j20524952058534" to-iso="+0923-12-22">梁</date>京兆西明寺<persName key="A011638">慧則</persName>傳（<persName key="A011640">元表</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0809a12"/><persName key="A011638">釋慧則</persName>，姓糜氏，<placeName key="PL000000010176">吳郡崑山</placeName>人也。<date key="j20289602029324" from-iso="+0843-01-01" to-iso="+0843-12-31">九歲</date>，博遊才<lb
ed="T" n="0809a13"/>義，總翫儒經。善種發萌，條然<ptr target="#n485"/>厭俗，以<date from-iso="+0853-02-16" key="j20326592033012" to-iso="+0854-02-04"><name>大中</name><lb
ed="T" n="0809a14"/>七年</date>就京<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明寺</placeName>出家。勤知諷誦，皆如曾<lb
ed="T" n="0809a15"/>習。<date from-iso="+0855-01-26" key="j20333682033751" to-iso="+0856-02-13">九年</date>於<placeName key="PL000000042216">本寺</placeName>承恩得度。<date from-iso="+0860-01-31" key="j20351992035523" to-iso="+0860-12-20">十四年</date>，棲<persName key="A009180">法寶大<lb
ed="T" n="0809a16"/>師</persName>法席覆講，<date from-iso="+0860-01-31" key="j20351992035523" to-iso="+0860-12-20">當年</date>勅補備員大德。<date from-iso="+0862-02-07" key="j20359372036290" to-iso="+0863-01-26"><name>咸通</name>三年</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0809a17"/>就崇聖寺<!--找不到此地-->講《俱舍論》并《喪服儀》，出《三界圖》一<lb
ed="T" n="0809a18"/>卷。<date from-iso="+0866-01-25" key="j20373852037768" to-iso="+0867-02-12">七年</date>，於祖院<!--找不到此地-->代<persName key="A009180">暢師</persName>講。<date from-iso="+0874-01-26" key="j20403082040636" to-iso="+0874-12-20">十五年</date>，勅署臨<lb
ed="T" n="0809a19"/>壇正員。<date from-iso="+0880-02-18" key="j20425222042876" to-iso="+0881-02-06"><name>廣明</name>元年</date>，巢寇犯闕，<placeName key="PL000000042002">關中</placeName>俶擾，出<lb
ed="T" n="0809a20"/><placeName key="PL000000043316">華州</placeName><placeName key="PL000000043289">下邽</placeName>避亂。<date from-iso="+0882-01-27" key="j20432312043614" to-iso="+0883-02-14"><name>中和</name>二年</date>，至<placeName key="PL000000010798">淮南</placeName>，<persName key="A008497">高公駢</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0809a21"/>召於法雲寺<!--找不到此地-->。講罷還<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳</placeName>，刺史<persName key="A011639">楊公</persName>苦留，却<lb
ed="T" n="0809a22"/>遊天台山<placeName key="PL000000014664">國清寺</placeName>挂錫。<date from-iso="+0894-02-14" key="j20476322047985" to-iso="+0895-02-02"><name>乾寧</name>元年</date>至明州<lb
ed="T" n="0809a23"/><placeName key="PL000000012309">育王寺</placeName>，撰《塔記》一卷，出《集要記》十二卷。<persName key="A003552">武肅<lb
ed="T" n="0809a24"/>王錢<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>命於<placeName key="PL000000013239">越州</placeName>臨壇。以<date key="j20529542052954" when-iso="+0908-09-11"><name>開平</name>二年八月<lb
ed="T" n="0809a25"/>八日</date>示疾坐亡。受生七十四，法臘五十四。<lb
ed="T" n="0809a26"/>窆于<placeName key="PL000000012279">鄮山</placeName>之岡。八戒弟子<anchor xml:id="beg0809sgsz2"/>刺<anchor xml:id="end0809sgsz2"/>史<persName key="A007285">黃晟</persName>營塔。<lb
ed="T" n="0809a27"/><persName key="A011638">則</persName>生常不好<anchor xml:id="beg0809001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>許</sic><corr>訐</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0809001"/>直，以撝謙推人為上。除<lb
ed="T" n="0809a28"/>講貫<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1247"/>外，輪誦經呪，自《法華》已降可三四十<lb
ed="T" n="0809a29"/>本，以資口業。覽大藏教兩遍，講鈔七十遍，<pb ed="T" n="0809b" xml:id="T50.2061.0809b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0809b01"/>《俱舍》、《喪儀》、《論語》各數遍。清苦執持，近苦罕有。<lb
ed="T" n="0809b02"/>入室弟子<persName key="A010005">希覺</persName>最露鋒頴焉。又<persName key="A011640">元表</persName>者，貞諒<lb
ed="T" n="0809b03"/>之士也，言多峭直，好品藻人事，而高義解<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g544"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0809b04"/>從習毘尼，兼勤外學，書史方術，無不該覽。<lb
ed="T" n="0809b05"/>早預京師<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明寺</placeName><persName key="A009180">法寶大師</persName>講肆，迨<date notBefore-iso="+0880-02-18" key="j20425222043063" notAfter-iso="+0881-08-12"><name>廣明</name>中</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0809b06"/><placeName key="PL000000023581">神都</placeName>版蕩，遂出<placeName key="PL000000000197">江表</placeName>，居越州<placeName key="PL000000013226">大善寺</placeName>，講《南<lb
ed="T" n="0809b07"/>山律鈔》。諸郡學人，無不趨集。表義理縱橫，<lb
ed="T" n="0809b08"/>善其談說，每揮<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>塵</sic><corr>麈</corr></choice>柄，聽者忘疲，號<persName key="A011640">鑑水<lb
ed="T" n="0809b09"/><anchor xml:id="beg0809sgsz4"/>闍黎<anchor xml:id="end0809sgsz4"/></persName>。著《義記》五卷，亦號《鑑水》。出門人<persName key="A011641">清福</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0809b10"/>冠其首焉。</p>
